      <title>Piper Sandler 研究显示拜登获胜将推高美国收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/biden-win-to-push-us-yields-higher-piper-sandler-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Piper Sandler &amp; Co. 策略师表示，如果总统乔·拜登今年 11 月赢得连任，美国 10 年期国债收益率可能上升约 12 个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/biden-win-to-push-us-yields-higher-piper-sandler-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 19:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以太 ETF 即将获得美国批准，伦敦推出加密货币 ETN</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/ether-etfs-inch-closer-to-us-approval-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国证券交易委员会为以太坊 ETF 铺平道路，伦敦证券交易所推出一批与比特币和以太坊挂钩的 ETN。彭博社的 Emily Graffeo 和 Emily Nicolle 报道了这一消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/ether-etfs-inch-closer-to-us-approval-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 19:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
